branchCategory.name: Rodless Cylinder, CY1F, Magnetically Coupled - Low Profile Guide
branchCategory.description: <p>The CY1F low profile Rodless Cylinder - Magnetically Coupled uses industrial strength magnets located in the piston and external carriage to form a single unit that will travel when actuated with air pressure. It is installed with a single axis internal linear guide to reduce its profile as much as 29% and up to 50% weight reduction compared to the CY1H Series.</p>
